title: Super Green Beret # 1-2 (Lightning Comics)
description:
Action like no action ever before!
That cover blurb kid you not!

This is about a shrimpy guy in a red sweater who can turn into Super Green Beret when putting on a beret and doing the salute! Sounds a bit like Captain Marvel? Well it's the same creator!

With a panache that would make John Wayne shy, Super Green Beret beat up Vietcong, Fidel Castro and even Adolf Hitler in two chunky issues published by Lightning Comics in 1967

It's not terrible political correct, but the Comics Code must have approved

Read the books, then pick up your jaw from the floor
